Create bottom left chart in Non Graded 43

Step 1: Create bottom left chart in Non Graded

- Copy and Paste the chart we just created.

Select formatting under general, X position = 221, Y position = 435, Width = 576, Height = 284




- Move the field CourseName to second position in the top chart.

- Remove ClassName from the bottom left chart and move Course Name into the second position.

- Remove Ungraded in Queue and Submissions per Day, add Ungraded per Day into the column value field. You will remove the period at the beginning of the field.

- Change the title to Ungraded per Day, Avg Non Graded Days
